version_description: The prologue to Twilight, from the Album Time.
Easy to read, complete and accurate.
The same song but with easier chords which work for both the ELO studio recording and Jeff Lynne's Bungalow Recording.

Complete intermediate version / including instrumental parts / short tab for intro and interludes / suggestions for voicings of special chords / ukulele demo of this chord sheet: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fC1zCJKG6RE.
Complete chords and lyrics / intermediate with split chords and suggestions for voicings.
Complete chords and lyrics / convenient auto-scrolling.
